This paper deals with the privacy implications of online advertising and proposes a methodology for computing the price paid for an individual's personal data. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.DB (Databases), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
